Add Mac and Windows setup scripts; fix cross-platform Chrome history path

- setup.sh renamed to setup-linux.sh
- setup-mac.sh: venv setup + optional launchd user agent (--service flag)
  handles Homebrew Python on both Apple Silicon and Intel
- setup-windows.ps1: venv setup for Windows; uses py/python3/python
  launcher discovery; prints Task Scheduler guidance for auto-start
- app.py: Chrome history path now resolved per platform (Linux, macOS,
  Windows) instead of hardcoded Linux path
